data.meta_description: 416 likes, 11 comments - bay_area_nostalgia on June 5, 2024: "“In 1965 Dornacker vied to become San Francisco State University’s Homecoming Queen. Her campaign saw her riding a bicycle enclosed in a cage; she described herself as an ‘Earth Mother’ and declared that she was magic. Although she won election to the position, she withdrew stating that she ‘didn’t want the responsibility’.”". Wacky, outrageous, sensitive, sweet, gentle
